query:
SELECT P.CODPROD, LTRIM(RTRIM(P.DESCRPROD)) AS DESCRPROD, LTRIM(RTRIM(P.UNIDADE)) AS UNIDADE, LTRIM(RTRIM(P.MARCA)) AS MARCA, P.NCM, SUM(ISNULL(E.ESTOQUE,0)) AS TOTAL_ESTOQUE
FROM [SANKHYA].[TGFEST] E
JOIN [SANKHYA].[TGFPRO] P ON P.CODPROD = E.CODPROD
WHERE E.CODLOCAL = 101010
GROUP BY P.CODPROD, P.DESCRPROD, P.UNIDADE, P.MARCA, P.NCM
ORDER BY P.DESCRPROD;
originalQuery:

FROM [SANKHYA].[TGFEST] E
JOIN [SANKHYA].[TGFPRO] P ON P.CODPROD = E.CODPROD
WHERE E.CODLOCAL = 101010

ORDER BY P.DESCRPROD;
